usuario.bio: Sou o João tenho 20 anos, curso análise e desenvolvimento de sistemas na puc São Gabriel e tenho o desejo de me tornar um desenvolvedor.

series.title: Venom: The Last Dance
series.overview: Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
